3. After one and a half years as an ISNE student, make some recommendations to prospective ISNE students. (Your answer must be at least 50 words long)

**Answer: Difficult from the beginning or maybe until the end, haha. The first period is an adaptation period because all subjects are in English. may have to try harder to understand But when it's over Moving on to the next step was not difficult. All subjects use comprehension. Program subjects also require frequent familiarization exercises. The subjects that focus on memorization mainly focus on reading or the main idea. As for the calculation, it's difficult to pass, haha, because I haven't passed yet.
